<sect1 id="dir_dce1906995fc04bc1dbe3a024e8fe6d5_1autotoc_md11">
<title>Instalación</title><para><orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Clonar el repositorio</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Crear entorno virtual: <computeroutput>python -m venv venv</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Activar entorno: <computeroutput>source venv/bin/activate</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Instalar dependencias: <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacepip" kindref="compound">pip</ref> install -r requirements.txt</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Configurar variables de entorno: <computeroutput>cp .env.example .env</computeroutput></para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Ejecutar: <computeroutput>python -m <ref refid="namespaceapp_1_1main" kindref="compound">app.main</ref></computeroutput></para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
